The paper presents a novel approach to regression of quantum mechanical energies using a scattering transform, which is a deep convolution network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves numerical experiments, which suggests that it may also belong to the computational engineering (cs.CE) and numerical analysis (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with quantum mechanics, which suggests that it may also belong to the scientific computing (cs.SD) sub-category.
